channel.title: Godzrsps 317 || Looking for a development team!
channel.description:
[ul][center][img]http://i.imgur.com/fIWvS33.gif[/img] [It's all about LEGENDS][/center]
[u]Introduction: [/u] We are a server called GoDzRSPS. We have worked hard to get the server up and running, and have put a lot of work into the game like there is no other. Also, we have a great team who are working day and night to keep the server fun, active and great to play.We want our players to have the best game experience they ever wanted and searched for! We even have a wiki that has a lot of guides to help if you are stuck with something and there is a lot of useful information to in expand your knowledge about the game. In our staff team we have got people who have been in the project since we started it all of them have a great RSPS experience and knowledge of RSPS. So with a great game and great staff team we are happy to invite YOU to join us and get the feeling of our server, And where you want to be all day and night long to become the LEGEND of our server. Our community is like no other! As soon as you join you will notice our active wilderness, active forums, and active PvMing and Clanning communities. Here at GoDzRSPS RuneScape Private Server, we don’t like to mess around, we want to bring you the players the best possible experience that we can give you. Our community gives a warm welcome to all new players, and presents them with many opportunities to get involved with activities and get to know existing members. We have many events and tournaments in and out of the wilderness that makes this possible. These can be anything from Clan based PKing, to a simple game of Hide and Seek.
[u]WE'RE RECURTING![/u]
I'm looking for a decent development team
This is what i am looking for [list] [li]Websitedeveloper 0/1[/li][/list] [list][li]Coder 0/3[/li][/list] [list][li]Graphicdesigner 0/2[/li][/list]
[u] Contact information[/u] PM me on forums if you have any questions or if you would like to join the development team[/ul]
